    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>This recipe takes around 5-10 min to prep, so get your ingredients ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-and-mustard-glazed-sausage-baguette-with-sweet-potato-wedges/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your<strong> potato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-and-mustard-glazed-sausage-baguette-with-sweet-potato-wedges/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> onion wedges</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> (or two!) with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong>, a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>honey </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Scrunch the foil around the <strong>onion wedges</strong> to form a tightly sealed parcel and add to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Add your <strong>sausages </strong>to the tray[s] and put in the oven for 20-25 min or until the sausages are cooked through (no pink meat!) and the onions are softened</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-and-mustard-glazed-sausage-baguette-with-sweet-potato-wedges/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>potato wedges </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to another <strong>baking paper-</strong>lined baking tray (or two!)<strong> </strong>and put in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-and-mustard-glazed-sausage-baguette-with-sweet-potato-wedges/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Mix the <strong>remaining honey </strong>with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>wholegrain mustard </strong>in a small bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>honey & mustard glaze</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>wholegrain</strong> <strong>mustard </strong>in a large bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is you<strong> mustard slaw</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-and-mustard-glazed-sausage-baguette-with-sweet-potato-wedges/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the sausages are cooked, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Spoon the <strong>honey & mustard glaze </strong>over the sausages and return to the oven for a final 2-3 min or until the sausages are sticky \u2013 these are your <strong>honey & mustard glazed sausages</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-and-mustard-glazed-sausage-baguette-with-sweet-potato-wedges/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut a slit into the top of your <strong>baguette[s]</strong></p><p>Once the wedges are nearly ready, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>baguette[s] </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until warmed through and crusty</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/honey-and-mustard-glazed-sausage-baguette-with-sweet-potato-wedges/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>sausages </strong>in half<strong> </strong>diagonally</p><p>Fill the baguette with the <strong>sweet onions </strong>and <strong>honey & mustard glazed sausages </strong>and drizzle with the <strong>tomato ketchup</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>potato wedges </strong>and <strong>mustard slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
